word_mean_info__list.difference: 含义最广，侧重固有的仁爱，慷慨等高尚的美德。
指品格的纯正，有高度是非感的美德。
强调符合道德标准的行为或用道德准则衡量某事，尤注重男女间的道德品行。
一般用词，指符合道德准则的隐恶扬善行为或品行或指一种有意识去做善事的高尚道德。
普通用词，侧重为人忠厚，老实，正直，不欺骗，不说谎。
侧重办事或处事公正、公道不偏心。
指品格纯正，有高度是非感，正直诚实，受人敬佩。

bilingual.target: 每个国家都非常重视其领土完整。

bilingual.source: Protecting territorial integrity is a fundamental duty of a nation.
bilingual.target: 维护领土完整是国家的基本职责。

bilingual.source: The Confucian philosophy emphasizes moral integrity and social harmony.
bilingual.target: 儒家哲学强调道德完整和社会和谐。

bilingual.source: Any action that infringes on territorial integrity is unacceptable.
bilingual.target: 任何侵犯领土完整的行为都是不可接受的。

bilingual.source: Their foreign policy emphasizes the importance of territorial integrity.
bilingual.target: 他们的外交政策强调了领土完整的重要性。

bilingual.source: The dmu ensures data integrity and security.
bilingual.target: 数据管理单元确保数据的完整性和安全性。

bilingual.source: You can verify the integrity of the file with gpg.
bilingual.target: 你可以用gpg（GNU Privacy Guard，用于加密、数字签名及产生非对称钥匙对的软件）来验证文件的完整性。

bilingual.source: The engineer inspected the integrity of the conduit.
bilingual.target: 工程师检查了导管的完整性。
启用自动递增有助于维护数据完整性。

bilingual.source: This system uses odd parity to ensure data integrity.
bilingual.target: 这个系统采用奇校验来确保数据的完整性。

list.abstract: integrity是一个英语单词，名词，作名词时意为“完整；正直；诚实；廉正”。

yingyinNormal.en: Exactly. And you owe it to yourself and to posterity to protect the genetic integrity of your sister's future offspring.
yingyinNormal.zh: 正是，并且你有责任替你自己和你子孙保留你妹妹所传后代遗传基因的完整性。

yingyinNormal.en: I think if it were exposed to a sufficiently powerful energy source something very similar to its own signature, perhaps its molecular integrity could fail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得如果它遭遇足够强大的能量源特性类似其本身的能量，那或许它的分子完整性就会被破坏。

yingyinNormal.en: Stratton Oakmont. Stability. Integrity. Pride.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯奥投资，稳健，诚实，自豪。

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, well, from st. jude's, I've learned integrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从圣·犹大学，我学会了诚实。

yingyinNormal.en: We have profits. They have integrity. I'm buying it!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有利润，他们有诚信，我要买下它！

yingyinNormal.en: Fidelity, bravery, and integrity. Correct. Now to business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 忠诚，勇敢，正直。回答正确，说正事吧。

yingyinNormal.en: The Dartmouth principles of community, highlight integrity, responsibility and consideration.
yingyinNormal.zh: 达特茅斯的校训强调诚实，责任和关怀。

yingyinNormal.en: See? That's why I like about this guy: integrity. Bring it in!
yingyinNormal.zh: 看到没？所以我才这么喜欢他：铁面无私。来抱一个！

yingyinNormal.en: Maya, you played fair. We didn't. We have no integrity. You do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛雅，你们公平竞争了，而我们没有，我们不诚信，你们和我们不一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Margaret Tilden used to have some integrity, Tom. And so did you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛格丽特·蒂尔顿当年没这么下作，汤姆，你也是。

yingyinNormal.en: Can you look into someone named Nelson Dubeck? He's with the Office of Public Integrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你能调查一下叫尼尔森·杜柏克的家伙吗？他在廉政办公室做事。

yingyinNormal.en: And people always ask me: "What's it take to be an RSM?" Leadership. Courage. Integrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人们经常问我 "怎么才能成为区域销售经理?" 领导才能、勇气、正直。

yingyinNormal.en: When I thought you wanted sex in exchange for this job, I said no. That shows integrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我以为你要我用性来交换工作，当时我拒绝了，这表示我有骨气。

yingyinNormal.en: So there you go, you got courage, you got integrity, you got courage again, and not litigious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你看，我有勇气、有骨气，双重勇气，而且又不告你。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, this cereal has lost all its molecular integrity. I now have a bowl of shredded wheat paste.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太棒了，这碗麦片再不彼此分子独立了，我现在有一碗麦片糊了。

yingyinNormal.en: This guy just backed out of a deal on me. If there's one thing I hate, it's a man without integrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这家伙说话不算话，我最痛恨不讲信用的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Check the structural integrity of the trophy case, bitches, 'cause mama's bringing home some hardware!
yingyinNormal.zh: 检查一下奖牌盒有没有坏，小表砸们，因为老娘又要带点家伙什回来了！

yingyinNormal.en: Without the politics and bureaucracy, that undermine the integrity of government run spy organizations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有政治和官僚主义，专门瓦解政府手下的间谍组织。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry, are you questioning my integrity as a scientist? If the lab room disposable shoe cover fits.
yingyinNormal.zh: 打断下，你是在质疑我作为科学家的诚信吗？实验室的一次性鞋套合脚吗？

yingyinNormal.en: My integrity is not for sale. Mine is. Maya! We owe your mother a hundred bucks. Put her there, partner!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的诚信不出售。我的出售。玛雅。我们欠你妈妈一百块钱呢。合作愉快，搭档。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: This type of <highlight>integrity</highlight> requires well-enforced laws in government transparency.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这类形式的廉正需要在政务管理透明化方面具备实施得力的法律。

examination_example.sentence: Two years ago, Rupert Murdoch's daughter, Elisabeth, spoke of the "unsettling dearth of <highlight>integrity</highlight> across so many of our institutions."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 两年前，Rupert Murdoch的女儿伊丽莎白说，“我们的许多机构都存在令人不安的诚信缺失”。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Integrity</highlight> had collapsed, she argued, because of a collective acceptance that the only "sorting mechanism" in society should be profit and the market.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她认为，诚信已经崩溃，因为人们普遍认为，社会中唯一的“分类机制”应该是利润和市场。
